build ./build/release/a/sound/format-au.o:  CompileA ./source/sound/format-au.c
build ./build/release/a/sound/format-wav.o: CompileA ./source/sound/format-wav.c
build ./build/release/a/sound/laws.o:       CompileA ./source/sound/laws.c
